name: Insites Design System
description:
Your journey to application nirvana starts by designing your application utilising our User Interface Design System, which has been carefully handcrafted in Figma, which would make your designer blush with excitement. There are hundreds of Design Elements available to create a stunning user experience, all while having the complete confidence that each one has been developed as a Code Element for your developers to use when it comes to bringing your beauty to life.


Need help using or modifying the Design System? View our documentation here.


Check out the code documentation for the components here.
